.Dd February 3, 1998
.Dt i4bctl 4
.Sh NAME
.Nm i4bctl
.Nd control device for the isdn4bsd kernel part
.Sh FreeBSD SYNOPSIS
.Cd pseudo-device \&"i4bctl\&"
.Sh NetBSD SYNOPSIS
none
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is used by the
.Xr isdndebug 8
utility to get and set the current debugging level and other information
of the isdn4bsd package kernel ISDN handling layers.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr isdndebug 8
